    <thetext>BoundFunctionCreate is unconditionally setting the [[Prototype]] of the bound function it creates to %FunctionPrototype%.  It should, instead set it to the [[Prototype]] of the target function.  Otherwise, binding a function (such as a class constructor or generator function causes it to loose access to inherited properties.</thetext>
